<h1>You are all set!</h1>

<p>
  The <%= @market.name %> Market Manager has activated your account and you are officially ready
  to shop the market. Log in to quickly and easily buy great food produced right near you.
</p>

<div class="lo_call_to_action">
  <a href="<%= root_url(host: (@market ? @market.domain : "app.#{ENV.fetch('DOMAIN')}")) %>" class="lo_button lo_button_large">Log in to Your Account</a>
  <p>
    If clicking the button doesn't work, right click it and copy the link.<br>
    After you've copied it, paste it into a new browser window.
  </p>
</div>
